<p>Hello <%= @user&.first_name %>,</p>
<p>
	We heard you need a password reset. Click the link below and you'll be redirected to a secure site from which you can set a new password.
</p>
<div>
	<%= link_to "Reset Password", "#{@domain}/reset-password?reset_token=#{@user.auth_token}", style: "color: #fff; background-color: #28608f; padding: 10px; text-decoration: none;" %>
</div>
<p>
	If you didn't try to reset your password then ignore this email.
</p>
<p>Thanks</p>
<p>HiveAPT Team</p>
